Introduction

Mingi is a South Korean rapper, dancer, singer, songwriter, producer, and composer under KQ Entertainment. He is a member of the boy group ATEEZ, in which he debuted on October 24, 2018 with the release of their first mini album "TREASURE EP.1: All to Zero".

Before debuting, Mingi appeared and competed on the survival show "MIXNINE" where he was eliminated after ranking 113rd.
